Subject: [PATCH 05/12] 005-canvas-fingerprint

Canvas fingerprint noise via --aspect-canvas-noise-seed:
- getImageData path: base_rendering_context_2d.cc
- toDataURL/toBlob path: image_data_buffer.cc
- Both use edge-pixel-flip algorithm with deterministic seed
---
